  1→/**
  2→ * Changes View — Self-contained diff viewer for the Changes content tab.
  3→ *
  4→ * Two layout modes (persisted per workspace):
  5→ * - Minimap (default): full-width diff viewer + thin colored strip on right edge.
  6→ *   Hovering the strip reveals a floating file tree panel.
